title: Re-attach detached GridItems when opening grid, closed #18

Re-attach detached GridItems when opening grid, closed #18

A GridItem isn't deleted anymore when deleting its plugin object. Instead, we save the pluginPageUrl attribute when creating a GridItem, and "-1" as pluginId attribute once we delete the plugin.

  Then, when opening a grid, we check if we can reattach every detached GridItem. If not, we display a "broken" image instead.
